sh Corner Sofa Beds","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_kx4FxV":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Create a cosy haven for relaxation and entertainment with our range of <strong>L-shaped sofa beds<\/strong>. These corner sofa designs combine the comfort of a spacious 3-seater sofa with the added benefit of a pull-out double bed, making it easy to accommodate unexpected guests. <\/p><p><strong>Types of Corner Sofa Beds:<\/strong><\/p><p>1. Right Corner Sofa Bed<\/p><p>2. Left Corner Sofa Bed<\/p><p><\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_awmkKi","text_kx4FxV"],"custom_css":[".section__block.section__block--heading {font-size: 30px; color: #806642;}",".section__block.reading-width p {line-height: 1.8; font-size: 16px; color: #555;}"],"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Mink-Crush-Corner-Sofabed-Stool.png","video_external":"","video_description":"","video_autoplay":false,"layout":"left","image_fit":"contain","media_width":50,"media_scale":100,"text_align":"text-start","color_scheme":"none"}},"media_with_text_3AQ7n6":{"type":"media-with-text","blocks":{"heading_adx67d":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Why Choose a Corner Sofa with Storage?","heading_size":"h3","heading_h1":false}},"text_7pq4dG":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>A <strong>corner sofa with storage<\/strong> is more than just a place to sit - it's an all-in-one solution for creating a clutter-free, functional living area. The storage features help you organise your space efficiently, while the corner design maximises seating without taking up unnecessary floor space. Whether you're looking for extra room to store pillows, throws, or everyday items, these sofas are the perfect way to keep your space neat and tidy without compromising on style or comfort.<\/p><p>Discover the ultimate in comfort, convenience, and storage with our <strong>corner sofas with storage<\/strong> today!<\/p>","enlarge_text":false}}},"block_order":["heading_adx67d","text_7pq4dG"],"c